Author: hoanghai
Title: [ANN][ICO] Instant Assests Tokens (IAT) - Revolutionizing the Real Estate Market
Body: Real estate investing has been one of the most profitable ventures known to man. Totalling up the global property value (inclusive of residential, commercial, industrial and agricultural land), the market cap is a staggering value of above US$210 trillion with residential property making up about 75% of it. However, getting into the market has not been the easiest for the masses for various  reasons such as: ‚Ä¢ High capital requirements ‚Ä¢ Stringent financial regulations to gain access to mortgages ‚Ä¢ Restrictions on foreign ownership ‚Ä¢ High upfront charges and taxes on resale ‚Ä¢ Clear ownership transfer ‚Ä¢ Lack of transparency in the entire process framework which is especially  so in developing countries With the introduction of Instant Assets Tokens (IAT), the company aims to make property investment easily available to the masses through the digitization of assets. The company has plans to expand to other developing countries with focus first being placed on the Philippines market.

Author: hoanghai
Title: [ANN][ICO] Instant Assests Tokens (IAT) - Revolutionizing the Real Estate Market
Body: The NIAT will be the local token equivalent of the IA Tokens. It will reside within each individual real estate market and is pegged against the country‚Äôs native currency. As such, each country will have its own NIAT. It will not be minted on its own and can only be purchased using IA Tokens. This is to ensure that end users are not being exposed to the volatility of the cryptocurrency markets.

Author: Digitokens
Title: [ANN][ICO] Instant Assests Tokens (IAT) - Revolutionizing the Real Estate Market
Body: Hi,  Our plan is to target the developing countries in S.E.A. first as such countries pose a similar set of problems that the IAT platform can solve. At the moment, we will be launching the platform first in the Philippines market since we have already been in business here for the last 6 years. The next destination will be determined after our team has done the research and analysis post-ICO. The role of the token will be utility based and can also be used to purchase goods and services from our partner merchants.  With regards to benefits of hodl, we feel that the market has progressed and matured to a stage where the crypto community is beginning to realize that the business of the company post-ICO is very important now in determining the sustainability, long term benefits and value of the tokens. As such, we are confident that as long as the business is running well and delivering, the benefits to hodl will definitely be there as well.

Title: [ANN][ICO] Instant Assests Tokens (IAT) - Revolutionizing the Real Estate Market
Body: Hi,  Thank you for the support towards our IAT project. In the crypto space currently, we feel that there is a lack of real estate project that really tackles the issues faced by the industry as most projects have been really just focusing on the crowdfunding aspect of real estate. Though there are some that have a similar cause which is good for the industry but our focus is quite different as we are focused on the developing countries in S.E.A with most of these countries posting GDP growth of close to 7% and we have existing property investment and management businesses in the Philippines for the last 6 years. As such, we believe that the project presents an opportunity with a different focus on the real estate market.

Author: Digitokens
Title: [ANN][ICO] Instant Assests Tokens (IAT) - Revolutionizing the Real Estate Market
Body: The priority would be to develop the IAT Platform to cater to the various functions of a traditional real estate industry with IA Token. As for asset acquisition, it will be more of a mid-long term plan and acquisition can be in the form of residential, commercial or even joint-development with developers or land owners.  Acquisition will also be done over careful planning where assets acquired will be for revenue generation rather than a "quick flip" of the assets for profits.  Also, we hope to position the IAT Platform such that it will be ready to work with government bodies when they are open to using the Blockchain for actual asset ownership transfer. At the moment, any real estate transfer over Blockchain are mostly just transfer of rights rather than the actual ownership of it.

Author: Digitokens
Title: [ANN][ICO] Instant Assests Tokens (IAT) - Revolutionizing the Real Estate Market
Body: Hi,  IAT is an ERC20 compatible token and we differentiate ourselves from others in that we are:  - Targeting specifically developing countries which have been largely untapped. - We have existing businesses running in the Philippines for the last 6 years which is why we are launching the platform here first before expanding it to other developing countries - We have an existing property management business that is registered in the Philippines - Most of the developing countries in South East Asia are posting GDP forecast of close to 7% this year - Philippines is considered to be the highest revenue source for traditional channels like Airbnb in its developing countries segment  Lastly, we pride ourselves in the that we have been operating in the Philippines real estate market for the last 6 years and have established a wide network within the industry. That is also the reason why we were able to tie down multiple partnership including one with one of the biggest real estate agency in the Philippines, Land Asia who has under its management about 5,000 agents and brokers.  This is an excellent partnership as we will be able to tap into the agents and brokers network of clients to gain access to the home owners segment. As the portal will cater to the various segment of the real estate industry, the agents, brokers and home owners will be the top revenue generating groups of users.  We believe that going forward, crypto enthusiast like you will be looking at not just a MVP or finished product but the fact that the project will eventually be profitable in its business operations so that IA Tokens will be sustainable and have a long term prospect to it.  Thank you for your interest and I hope the above answers your questions.

Author: Digitokens
Title: [ANN][ICO] Instant Assests Tokens (IAT) - Revolutionizing the Real Estate Market
Body: We are not in the business of construction but instead property management. There are in fact lots of developers here in the Philippines, SMDC, Ayala, Federal Land, Megaworld, DMCI and Vista Land are just some of the bigger developers here in the Philippines. In recent times, more investors and developers from China have also been flocking in due to the property market boom and the fact that the country's master plan of the "Entertainment City - Las Vegas of Asia" in the region of Pasay have also served as a major magnet for property development.  Our office is located in Metro Manila, Makati. In fact, both our founders will be in our Manila office next week. Raymond from the 30th and Bryan from 28th. Let us know if you would like to drop by and they'll be happy to have a chat with you; not forgetting the soft drink of course.  The address of our office is 5th Floor, Unit 503 One Corporate Plaza 845 Antonio Arnaiz Ave Legazpi Village Makati City
